room_title: Escape room "The Millionaire Murder Escape" by Times Up! Escape Rooms in Raleigh - Durham
room_address: 216 E. Chatham St., Suite 108, Cary, NC 27511
room_description: You have been invited to the reading of the will for the renowned millionare Freddrick Trummel, but it turns out to be a sting operation for the capture of his murderer. Your only chance for freedom is to solve the murder and escape the room before the police arrive.
